    "The remainder of the paper is organized as follows: \"Background\" summarizes the most important machine learning (ML) and DL concepts.",
    "After that, \"Related work: machine learning in EEG analysis\" discusses relevant literature.",
    "Next, the \"Methods\" section provides an overview of the data, XAI pipeline, and conventional analysis methods used in this study.",
    "In the \"Results\" section, we present the outcomes of these different methods, and in the \"Discussion\" section, we critically reflect on them.",
